

| ChatGPT (browser)                       | OpenAI API (chatgpt CLI)                  |
| --------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| Uses **ChatGPT credits** from Plus plan | Uses **API billing account**              |
| Unlimited GPT-4 (within limits)         | Billed per token (unless you have credit) |
| No API key needed                       | Needs `sk-...` API key                    |
| Not the same billing system             | Separate from Plus                        |

| Feature               | ChatGPT (browser) | `chatgpt` CLI          | `codex` CLI                |
| --------------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Uses API credits?     | ‚ùå No              | ‚úÖ Yes                  | ‚úÖ Yes                      |
| Needs API key?        | ‚ùå No              | ‚úÖ Yes                  | ‚ùå (if using `codex login`) |
| Needs payment method? | ‚úÖ For Plus plan   | ‚úÖ For API access       | ‚úÖ (for extra API usage)    |
| Free credits?         | ‚ùå Not applicable  | ‚ùå Not by default       | ‚úÖ (\$5 for Plus users)     |
| Focus / use case      | Chat in browser   | Prompt from terminal   | Coding in terminal         |
| Maintainer            | OpenAI            | Community (unofficial) | OpenAI (official)          |



