ez a "codex" ez 5$ erejeig benne van a Plus elofizetesben
sudo npm install -g @openai/codex`
codex login
or 
export OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-your-secret-key"
echo $OPENAI_API_KEY
codex

| Task                       | Command / Steps                               |
| -------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| **Install CLI**            | `npm install -g @openai/codex`                |
| **Authenticate (ChatGPT)** | `codex login` ‚Üí choose "Sign in with ChatGPT" |
| **Authenticate (API Key)** | `export OPENAI_API_KEY="..."`                 |
| **Run CLI Suggest mode**   | `codex --approval-mode suggest "‚Ä¶" `          |
| **Use auto-edit mode**     | `codex --approval-mode auto-edit "‚Ä¶" `        |
| **Use full-auto mode**     | `codex --approval-mode full-auto "‚Ä¶" `        |
| **Specify model**          | `codex --model gpt-4.1 "‚Ä¶" `                  |
| **Use image input**        | `codex --image "path.png" "‚Ä¶" `               |


Launch in interactive mode:
codex

or

codex --approval-mode suggest "Explain this function in detail"
codex --approval-mode auto-edit "Refactor this file for readability"
codex --approval-mode full-auto "Fix build errors across the project"

codex --model gpt-4.1 "Generate unit tests for `main.py`"

codex --image "screenshot.png" "Create a similar webpage in HTML/CSS"



| Feature / Tool               | üß† **ChatGPT (browser)**        | üí¨ **`chatgpt` CLI**                                                 | üõ†Ô∏è **`codex` CLI**                                     |
| ---------------------------- | ------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| Interface                    | Web GUI                         | Terminal (unofficial tool)                                           | Terminal (official OpenAI CLI)                          |
| Auth method                  | OpenAI account (Plus/Free)      | OpenAI API Key (`sk-...`)                                            | `codex login` (OAuth) or API Key                        |
| Billing source               | ChatGPT subscription (Plus/Pro) | API billing account (tokens = \$)                                    | API billing or free promo credits (e.g. \$5)            |
| Free usage                   | Limited GPT-4 (with Plus)       | Only if API credits exist                                            | \$5 credit (Plus), \$50 (Pro) for 30 days (if eligible) |
| Uses OpenAI API              | ‚ùå No                            | ‚úÖ Yes                                                                | ‚úÖ Yes                                                   |
| Models available             | GPT-3.5, GPT-4 (via Plus)       | GPT-3.5, GPT-4                                                       | Codex models (codex-mini), GPT-4.5 (in beta)            |
| Designed for code assistance | ‚ö†Ô∏è Not specialized              | ‚ùå General Q\&A only                                                  | ‚úÖ Full coding assistant                                 |
| File editing                 | ‚ùå No                            | ‚ùå No                                                                 | ‚úÖ Yes (auto/suggest modes)                              |
| Runs shell commands          | ‚ùå No                            | ‚ùå No                                                                 | ‚úÖ Yes (with confirmation or full-auto mode)             |
| Supports ChatGPT Plus login  | ‚úÖ Native                        | ‚ùå Requires API key manually                                          | ‚úÖ With `codex login`                                    |
| Needs manual API key         | ‚ùå No                            | ‚úÖ Yes                                                                | ‚ùå No (if logged in with ChatGPT)                        |
| Open-source                  | ‚ùå No                            | ‚úÖ Yes ([GitHub](https://github.com/transitive-bullshit/chatgpt-cli)) | ‚úÖ Yes ([GitHub](https://github.com/openai/codex))       |
| Persistent config file       | N/A                             | `~/.chatgpt.json`                                                    | Stored internally via OAuth                             |












